social_posts.post_text: Yup - It’s happening! More #WeddingVeil magic is coming your way soon. We are having such a blast filming these movies. So grateful for @thereallacey @autumn_reeser & @hallmarkchannel for making this possible! #dreamscometrue #setlife #friends

So grateful for the incredible opportunities that have brought me to this moment.  Thank you @hallmarkchannel & of course @thereallacey for including me in this beautiful project (& taking this photo!). More #weddingveil stories are coming to you in January. #tuesdayvibes #gratitude

Even while I’m away filming on location - Christmas cheer is everywhere! Thanks to my friend @jen_lilley There is a wonderful way to give back during the season. Check out @christmasisnotcancelled for all the details! #christmasuniversity #christmas

I am so grateful to have such incredibly supportive friends!! We were filming late together on a night which happened to be the premiere of  #amagicalchristmasvillage . So while we were filming #theweddingveil everyone cozied up to watch and enjoy the movie during our breaks in between takes. @autumn_reeser @thereallacey @_misterpaul_ & @wardrobegirls_ were cheering on every scene. Gave me all the feels. ☺️ also, it’s airing again on @hallmarkchannel TODAY at 2pm  eastern if you haven’t seen it yet!!🎄🧑‍🎄

Glad no one is here to watch me doing my hotel room workouts. Lol. I’m sure i look ridiculous. I get really into it! 😂 But I am so lucky my bestie gave me this awesome vr system because it’s so much fun and such a great workout. 💪 Today was rock climbing and boxing. #fitness #workout #sunday #travel

One more week of filming on #TheWeddingVeil and they are premiering Jan 7th. That’s cutting it close, to be sure. 😉 But I’m not worried. Everyone has taken such care to make sure these movies are so special. I’m having so much fun working with @iamvictorwebster again!!

It has been so much fun filming #TheWeddingVeil in Greece 🇬🇷 & Bulgaria 🇧🇬 ! Every day has been such an incredibly fun adventure. I’m so grateful to everyone on the cast & crew for making this shoot so special. The new movies premiere January 7th on @hallmarkchannel
Though it’s been a hectic December we are so ready for Christmas!! Wishing you all a wonderful holiday weekend. 🎄❤️🎄
So excited for 2023!! #TheWeddingVeil is back starting Jan 7th on @hallmarkchannel at 8 pm ET/PT. 🥂 #cheers #newyears

Here’s a sneak peek scene from the new #TheWeddingVeil movie premiering THIS SATURDAY!! The fabulous exec producer, @thereallacey also stars in this darling romantic story. I can’t wait for you all to watch. #sneakpeek #movie #tunein 🎥 💍

@thereallacey and I had so much fun this morning doing press about #TheWeddingVeil Expectations premiere Saturday night. So many behind-the-scenes stories and memories. @autumn_reeser & I couldn’t stop laughing during the 🍕 scene. You’ll have to tune in Saturday night to find out what I mean! @hallmarkchannel 8pm

Tonight’s the night!!! Tune in at 8 on @hallmarkchannel for an all new #TheWeddingVeil movie. expectations staring @thereallacey & @kevin_mcgarry_w with @autumn_reeser & me of course chiming in as best friends do… 💕 “to the veil!” 👰🏻‍♀️ ❤️

I can’t believe Megan is 14 years old! Where has the time gone? 🥹 She makes me laugh every day. I’m so proud of my brave, determined and independent daughter. Happy Birthday Megan!! #tbt #throwbackthursday #birthday #daughter

TONIGHT is the premiere of #TheWeddingVeil Inspiration on @hallmarkchannel ! I had so much fun being a part of this delightful movie starring @autumn_reeser & @_misterpaul_ - their beautiful love story gave me all the feels. 🥹 tune in tonight to enjoy it with us. #romance
We’re talking all about our incredible adventure filming #theweddingveil THURSDAY 1pm ET on @hallmarkchannel ‘s Facebook page! Join us!!

Traveling to Greece to film #theweddingveil was just another magical element of being a part of these movies. I am so grateful for the opportunity to work with @thereallacey @autumn_reeser & @iamvictorwebster. Joining the cast are @alexanderfln @chegrant007 @katerina_geronikolou - we were directed by the fabulous @ronoliver , dressed by the fabulous @wardrobegirls_ ! I just can’t wait for Saturday night to watch with all of you!
What can I say about these ladies?! Eternally grateful for their friendship. #TheWeddingVeil … what a Journey it’s been. ❤️
Yay!!! Can’t wait!! Tune in with me Saturday 8pm eastern on @hallmarkchannel #TheWeddingVeil
Sunrise snuggles with my beautiful mare, Molly. So grateful for this quiet time before the competition begins. #horseshow #morning #horsesofinstagram
An amazing round with Molly today. Fast & clean!

First week back on set for 2023. Excited for a new year of fun projects to film and I’m so grateful for each and every opportunity. Can’t wait to get the latest movies on your screens. More to come. 🎥 ❤️
Sunday morning tennis practice. Ben is teaching me how to play - slow going. lol. 🎾
Thanks to my friend @benjaminayres and the fabulous @romance__university sweatshirts for keeping me warm on this chilly day filming in Vancouver. #alumni #hallmark #romance #setlife

We tortured Ben to get a good birthday photo. Dave asked isn’t he too old for balloons? I said NEVER!!! 🎈 we just can’t believe Ben is turning 18 today. Even as a really little kid he’s always been kind and sincere.  As he grew through school we discovered that he’s also smart and thoughtful. But my favorite is his fantastic sense of humor - because he likes all the same 80s comedies as I do !! 😉 We can’t wait to see where he goes from here. We love you so much, Ben and we’re so proud of you. Happy birthday! 🥳 🎂

In case you haven’t heard …. We’re back!!! @cameronmathison & I are working on a new #HannahSwensen mystery with @barbaraniven & @hoganfilm ! 👩🏼‍🍳 and we can’t wait to enjoy another delicious whodunnit with you all. We’re so grateful to @hallmarkmovie & Joanne Fluke for these fun adventures!! 🔍
Hello Hannah!! #setlife #makeup #hair #wardrobe #action 🎥
Dave & I spent the afternoon working on our rose garden. We planted a few new plants and fertilized. We have some happy plants now! 🌹 ❤️
Happy St Patrick’s Day!!! 🍀 🐴
Enjoying a lovely family Easter brunch.

When you’re Sami it must be difficult to capture all your siblings in one photo. Lol. But here’s a little #memories #monday shout out to my dear if a bit complicated #days family tree. #nationalsiblingday 😂 @thegreg_vaughan @ericmartsolf @dayspeacock 📺 ⌛️

I am completely in love with our rose garden. Dave catches me watching YouTube videos about how to take care of roses.  The whole process has brought us such joy. Im happy to report our newest additions to the rose garden are blooming and thriving. 🌹 happy #nationalgardeningday #roses #outdoors #sunnies ☀️
Wow! Congrats to Ben! Tonight was his first ever performance on stage - and he was the lead in the school production of Macbeth! And he nailed it. So awesome! 👏👏👏 #proudparents 🎭
PREMIERES MAY 19th!! Can’t wait to share the latest Hannah installment with you all!! #murdermystery
It was a blast celebrating #mothersday with these delightful moms!! Thank you @sherrishowtv for inviting me to be a part of this wonderful group 💕
Happy Mother’s Day to my incredible mom! I use the lessons you taught me every day and I’m always grateful for the laughter and grit you passed along to your children (& grandchildren!) 💕

Join @cameronmathison @barbaraniven & I to hear about the all new Hannah Swensen Mystery : Carrot Cale Murder TODAY on Facebook Live Wednesday, 5/17 1pm ET (or 10am PT) 
Find us at Hallmark Movies & Mysteries‘ Facebook page.

social_posts.post_text: Tune in to an all new #hannahswensenmysteries TONIGHT! Carrot Cake Murder premieres on @hallmarkmovie 9/8c so much fun with @cameronmathison @barbaraniven @hoganfilm !!! 🔍🕵🏼‍♀️ 🥕
Lights , camera, action! Every movie needs a Red Nose Day. Get yours at rednoseday.org thank you @comicreliefus for helping provide books in schools and meals on tables. #rednoseday 🎥
Megan’s middle school commencement was tonight. High school here we come!!! 🥹🥹
Celebrating #nationalroséday ! #cheers
Here we go again!! Back on set filming another #HannahSwensen with my friend @cameronmathison !! #setlife 🎥

Celebrating family this Friday! So grateful to have my kids joining me while I’m filming in Vancouver. Such a joy to spend time with them during their summer vacation. #kids #family #momlife #setlife 🎥❤️

So grateful for our fantastic equestrian family in the north! Thank you @brentbalisky , @laurabalisky & @laurajanetidball for being so wonderful to Megan & I as we settle in. (And get used to riding in the rain. Lol) #horselife #equestrian #barnfriends 🐴 🐴
Happy Father’s Day to this incredible, loving & supportive husband and father. Thank you for all you do for our family. You’re the best! I love you ❤️
So exciting to be on set for the newest #HannahSwensen ! Proud to be producing another episode for these fun characters. #bluesocks  #motivationmonday #setlife 🎥

My new friend Joyce is definitely a card carrying member of @romance__university ! She loves the #WeddingVeil movies so much, she was inspired to host an event at her church where many women brought in their mothers, grandmother and even some great grandmothers wedding dresses. They did a fashion show and put them all on display for the whole community to enjoy. Her story and the joy they shared is just so beautiful! @thereallacey @autumn_reeser @wardrobegirls_ @beth_grossbard_productions - I knew you’d love hearing how these wonderful movies have brought people together to celebrate.
Any day in the Cookie Jar is a good day. Happy Wednesday! #HannahSwensen #setlife
Celebrating  our 23rd anniversary!  Time flies when you’re having fun. ❤️ 👰‍♀️
Megan & I had a blast competing in Canada 🇨🇦! So grateful for this incredible opportunity.
Fun mother/daughter hike. Basil was leading the way. Taylor Swift was discussed. #mondaymotivation #doglover #family
Friday night fun. I was promised popcorn 🍿 🎥
Traveling kind of weekend.  #ootd  #saturdayvibes ✈️ thanks to @michelemariepr & @jonesnewyork
Haha! Wipe out all the way. Ben had no trouble hanging on. Me not so much. 😂 Summer fun with Ben, Dave & some friends out at the lake. ☀️ 💦
Three generations of horse lovers. #horsesofinstagram ❤️🐴
Megan & Abracadabra have been magic together. So fun to see them Champions of 1.10 Ch Jumpers @thunderbirdshowpark such a fun show! Great photos by @sarashierphotography !
#Weekendvibes 🙏🙏 thanks @michelemariepr & @jonesnewyork
Ben’s starting his senior year and Megan’s now a freshman in high school. Where does the time go?? 🥹🥹 #backtoschool 📚

Thinking of the rescue dogs that have such a special place in our hearts I wanted to share a link to help @americanhumane who have been on the frontlines caring for animals in the aftermath of the Maui wildfires. If you would like to contribute to their grant to help Maui Humane Society provide critical aid please see the link in my bio. 🐈 🐶 ❤️
Your friendship means so much to me @kristianalfonso ! Happy birthday to a truly special human. 😘😘😘 (also, thanks @soapdigest for this photo! 📷 ⌛️ )

Dave and I had the wonderful opportunity to support the @chp1199foundation this weekend. This organization does so much - see link in bio - we are thrilled help. If you see a future for yourself in law enforcement visit @chpcareers to find out more! 💛💙
Another trip around the sun ☀️🥳
I can’t let #nationaldaughtersday go by without a shoutout to my beautiful, funny and talented firecracker. We love you so much Megan. 🥰
Congrats Ben, on getting accepted to your first choice university!! ⭐️⭐️ Sic ‘em Bears!
Family fun.
Love spending time with my roses. 🌹
Found this fun ol’ pic from behind the scenes in the Days ‘control booth’ with Ken Corday to celebrate the 58th anniversary of Days of Our Lives. Congratulations!! 🎉🍾
So happy to be back in the make up trailer. #glam #glamsquad 📺 🎥

A new fun tradition is this pie baking class before Thanksgiving. My friend and I made a fruit pie (peach,apple & berry) and I made a pecan pie. We learned some fun tricks about how to decorate with the pie crust dough. I tried braiding it. (See photos in my story) #baking #thanksgiving #pie 🥧

Decorating done!! So happy to have the tree up and ready for the holiday season 🎄
Any day spent with horses is a good day. ☀️🐴 💕

Celebrating Jane Austen’s birthday by sharing that my movie, #Love&Jane will premiere on @hallmarkchannel February 10th. #loveuary I’m so proud of this fun romantic comedy based on a lifelong love of everything Jane Austen. #janeausten #romcom
Such a fun night celebrating friends and this wonderful holiday season. 🌲 🧑‍🎄 #merrychristmas #holidays
Everyone in the holiday spirit. #christmastree #family
Ww wish you all good cheer today and to those celebrating, from our family to yours, a very merry Christmas!!! 🎄❤️
My second golf lesson. One of my goals for 2024 - always fun to learn new things.
Happy new year!!!

I was talked into hitting the golf course. Mostly I’m just happy that I managed to hit straight. And once or twice I had a for-real nice shot.  We had a lot of fun. Dave & Ben were very patient with me. ☺️ #sunnies #golf #familytime

Can’t believe we are one month away from the @hallmarkchannel premiere of Love & Jane. This movie has been a passion project right from the start. The writer/director #davidweaver came up with a brilliant story and when we pitched it to @epmy1013 & Hallmark, they felt the same. @jcallahan2518 and I are both  huge Jane Austen fans, so we completely bonded to honor Jane as much as we possibly can. Casting @benjaminayres was just perfect- he’s brought so much to this role. And I have to give a special shoutout to @jaralin & the @wardrobegirls_ . You all really helped me discover this character and set the brilliant tone for the whole movie with the costume design. 😘 thank you to you all! Thanks to @craig_baumgarten keeping us all in line - like wrangling cats out there on set. lol. But you helped us bring the vision to life. 📚 ❤️
Actress, director, producer and author.
